        {
          "expr": "shitbox_alt",
          "legendFormat": "Altitude",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 27
      },
      "title": "Day Narrative \u2014 $day",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "> _Auto-generated narrative goes here. Pulled from notes + events + driver-stats for the day._\n\n**Example shape**, populated post-drive:\n\n*\"Day 3, 487 km from Charters Towers to Longreach. Tony drove the morning into a headwind out of Pentland; Dani took the wheel after the lunch stop in Hughenden and pushed the pace through the long straights to Winton. Eight events captured: two HARD_BRAKE on the Flinders Highway descent, one BIG_CORNER through the Lochern bend, five HIGH_G hits crossing corrugations west of Winton. Two fuel stops, day average 9.2 km/L. No hardware degradation. Edward called twice from the back seat asking if we were there yet.\"*\n\n**Sources to wire (later):**\n- `notes.json` \u2014 extract free-text per day\n- `events.json` \u2014 group by type, attach location names from `_resolve_location`\n- `fuel.json` \u2014 list stops, compute day's running efficiency\n- `driver-stats.json` \u2014 per-driver time on the day\n- LLM rendering (or templated string fill) at the end\n\nThis is a placeholder while the design settles."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 33
      },
      "title": "Mock-up notes",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**This is a mock-up.** Layout is intentional; data wiring is partial.\n\n- **Working live:** Top Speed, Peak G, Events count, Fuel Stops, Fuel Used, Avg Efficiency, Notes count, Hardware health, Drive Time pie, Events-by-type bar, Speed & Altitude time-series.\n- **Wired but rough:** Distance (no `shitbox_trip_distance_km` metric yet \u2014 placeholder), Time Moving (count_over_time approximation, not minutes-precise), Geomap (single-trail, no event pins / fuel pin overlay).\n- **Placeholder:** Fuel Stops & Efficiency table, Day Narrative.\n- **Day picker:** the `$day` template variable is display-only. The time-range picker (top right) still drives queries \u2014 set it to the day's window manually for now. A small dashboard-script could bind them automatically; out of scope for the mock.\n\nDelete this panel before declaring the dashboard done."
      },
      "transparent": true
    }
  ]
